# Used for A detecting live object on object detection : Pin-High  
# (Body & live humun being)

# ðŸ’¥ CONNECTION 

Device Needs : 
1) Raspberry pi kit
2) LDR Sensor Module
3) Jumper Wires
4) LED light


LDR Sensor ->  Raspberry pi Connection :

+ve  : vcc    ->  Pin 2  : v5/vcc
data : input  ->  Pin 12 : GPIO 18
-ve  : ground ->  Pin 6  : ground 


LED Pin -> Raspberry pi Connection  :

-ve ->  ground 
+ve ->  Pin 18 (GPIO 24)

LED small leg - negative -: connect to ground 
LED long leg - positive -:  output pin



# ðŸ’¥ RASPBERRY PI  CODE

import RPi.GPIO as GPIO
import time
GPIO.setmode(GPIO.BCM)
GPIO.setup(24,GPIO.OUT) # pin 18
GPIO.setup(18,GPIO.IN) # pin 12
# here 18 & 24 are just pin name, not directly pin no.

while(True):
   myin=GPIO.input(18)
   if myin==True:
   print("Motion Detected")
   time.sleep(1)
   GPIO.output(24,True)
   time.sleep(0.5)
   GPIO.output(24,False)
   time.sleep(0.5)

